Add Rebirth / prestige system

Click the new neon "🔁 REBIRTH" pad on your plot to reset coins + building levels
in exchange for a PERMANENT +50% income multiplier (stacks per rebirth) and a
guaranteed Mythic card. Cards, cup progress, gems and game passes are kept.
Eligibility scales: 25 total building levels for the first rebirth, +25 each time.
Income (live + offline) and the HUD readout apply the multiplier.

